sentences.english: I have the great honor of being invited here.
sentences.chinese: 我很荣幸被除数邀请来这儿。

sentences.english: The divisor is subtracted from the dividend.
The man was seized as he left the building.
sentences.chinese: 这人在他离开这憧楼时被除数抓了。

sentences.english: In a division operation, the number or quantity by which the dividend is divided.
sentences.chinese: 在除法运算中，去除被除数的那个数或量。

definition: proper fraction (with numerator < denominator, e.g. five sevenths)/see also: improper fraction 假分數|假分数[jia3 fen1 shu4] and mixed number 帶分數|带分数[dai4 fen1 shu4]

mixed fraction/mixed number (i.e. with an integer part and a fraction part, e.g. four and three quarters)/see also: improper fraction 假分數|假分数[jia3 fen1 shu4] and proper fraction 真分數|真分数[zhen1 fen1 shu4]
